scribus-ng (1.5.4+dfsg-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version 1.5.4+dfsg.
    https://wiki.scribus.net/canvas/1.5.4_Release
    https://w.scribus.net/wiki/index.php/1.5.4_Release
  * d/upstream/signing-key.asc: Refresh.
  * Remove patches applied upstream.
  * d/control:
    + Bump Standards-Version to 4.1.4, no changes needed.
    + Move Vcs-* to salsa.debian.org.
    + Use HTTPS in the Homepage field.
    + Add new build-dependencies on libqxp-dev and libzmf-dev.
  * d/rules:
    + Use dh_missing instead of the deprecated dh_install --fail-missing.
  * Bump debhelper compat level to 11:
    + Remove --parallel, now default
  * d/scribus-ng.mime: remove: if it's needed I want it upstream first.
  * d/copyright:
    + Use HTTPS in the Source field.
    + Update.

