scribus-ng (1.5.1+dfsg-2) experimental; urgency=medium

  * [124d1dc] debian/patches/system-hyphen: backport patch from upstream to
    use /usr/share/hyphen as a system place to look up hyphenation dictionaries.
  * [ad29d5e] debian/scribus-ng-data.links: remove compat symlink to the system
    hyphenation dictionaries.
  * debian/control:
    + [09ce733] wrap-and-sort accordig to my new preferences.
    + make this more similar to the main scribus package:
      - [0267e4a] move to priority:extra.
      - [e9636ff] add missing build-dependency on dh-python.
      - [f70194f] recommend hyphen-hyphenation-patterns and fonts-dejavu.
      - [b5a6588] suggest scribus-ng-doc.
    + [6ac409d] update build dependencies to be sure every optional feature is
                enabled and drop obsolate version restrictions.
    + [3e84a4d] build-depend on libfreehand-dev instead of libfreehand-0.1-1.
  * Changes done to have all 3 scribus packages (scribus and scribus-{ng,trunk})
    both in their debian version (with non-dfsg file stripped) and upstream
    build out of the same debian/ directory as much as possible:
    + [a99238d,79f3a04] debian/rules: add some noop code.
    + [d2bdb96] use dh-exec parametrize the package name in d/*.{install,links}.
    + [4976aab] lintian-overrides: override dh-exec-subst-unknown-variable.

 -- Mattia Rizzolo <mattia@debian.org>  Tue, 22 Mar 2016 14:33:23 +0000

scribus-ng (1.5.1+dfsg-1) experimental; urgency=low

  * Adopt the package after long time.
  * [68c7080] Imported Upstream version 1.5.1+dfsg.  Closes: #788944
    https://wiki.scribus.net/canvas/1.5.1_Release
    https://w.scribus.net/wiki/index.php/1.5.1_Release
    + the hyphenation patterns are removed from the tarball, and the system
      libhyphen is used. Closes: #410093, #534509
  * [c2e990d] debian/README.source: rewrite.
  * debian/NEWS:
    + [6e3e185] fix debian-news-entry-uses-asterisk lintian tag.
    + [8c11cb7] new entry for 1.5.x.
  * debian/control:
    + [7485c82] Set myself as maintainer, thank malex for all the work done!
    + [839a518,bf4ff69,1c77129,501a2b0,9737b83] add lot of reletions to other
      packages (Build-Depends, Depends, Recommends, Suggests, etc).
    + [f7ccddb] fix homepage-in-binary-package lintian tag.
    + [0c925cd,fdb3752] add Vcs-* fields.
    + [e4ae168,0b02592,d74f2be] bump standards-version to 3.9.7.
    + [72db14b] use a useful short description.
    + [40e4ec2] drop some pointless fields.
  * debian/patches:
    + [5ccb6aa] remove_non-free_file.patch: add to fix FTBFS due to repack.
    + [34b299c] hyphen-used-as-minus-sign.patch: add.
    + [b662259] qreal_double.patch: add to fix FTBFS on arm* due to qreal/double
      clashes. I hope I have adapted the patch correctly...
    + [dcbd175] desktop.patch: add to edit the desktop file to call scribus-ng
      instead of scribus.
  * debian/copyright:
    + [7075c47,46f9af2] update and rewrite using copyright-format 1.0.
    + [dd83603] update years.
    + [de83f14] fix unused-file-paragraph-in-dep5-copyright lintian tag.
  * [05b35d0] debian/{compat,control} use dh9.
  * debian/rules:
    + [51068cf,ff68ab0,2a51a71,7321c4e] rewrite.
    + [100b967] allow installation of AUTHORS file.
    + [4edd4ac] pass -n option to gzip to allow reproducible builds.
    + [d8ce176] fix typos in ChangeLogScripts.
    + [1f43908] properly exclude the plugins from dh_fixperms.
      Thanks to Philip Muskovac for the idea.
    + [3fc8c1a] exclude the documentation from dh_compress.
  * [6f08ea5,c51ba63,b5db4f4] debian/scribus-ng.lintian-overrides: add to
    override a bunch of shlib-with-executable-bit.
  * [978e6e0] debian/pycompat: drop, not needed anymore.
  * [ba8dae2] Split the package into 2 binaries: scribus-ng, scribus-ng-data
    + Closes: #759132
    + debian/control: add scribus-data stanza, with appropriate
      relationshipts.
    + [5117400,093c220] debian/scribus-ng-data.install: add usr/share stuff.
    + debian/scribus-ng-data.links: add.
    + debian/scribus-ng.install: add with all usr/{bin,lib} stuff.
    + debian/scribus-ng.mime: add, not sure if it is useful.
    + debian/rules:
      - update all paths: from debian/scribus-ng/ to debian/tmp.
      - [e644b25] update configure options.
      - override dh_install to use the --fail-missing option.
    + [6f5f8f9] debian/scribus-ng{,-data}.install: install the .desktop file in
      /usr/share/applications in the scribus-ng binary.
  * [b0783a6] debian/watch: update and add upstream signing key.

 -- Mattia Rizzolo <mattia@debian.org>  Fri, 11 Mar 2016 16:28:00 +0000

